"title": "5624: witnesses, to Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5624",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The NT identifies a variety of witnesses to Jesus Christ, who confirm his identity and importance. It also stresses the importance of believers bearing witness to Christ in the world.</p>\n<h2>The witness of the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:22-Acts26:23\">ACT 26:22–26:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:39-John5:40\">JHN 5:39–5:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:2\">HEB 12:1–12:2</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of John the Baptist</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:6-John1:8\">JHN 1:6–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:1-Matt3:3\">MAT 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3\">ISA 40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:11-Matt3:12\">MAT 3:11–3:12</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:7-Mark1:8\">MRK 1:7–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:15-Luke3:18\">LUK 3:15–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:15\">JHN 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:19-John1:31\">JHN 1:19–1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:26-John3:30\">JHN 3:26–3:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:33-John5:35\">JHN 5:33–5:35</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">ACT 5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:6-1John5:9\">1JN 5:6–5:9</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of the Father</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:18\">JHN 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:37-John5:38\">JHN 5:37–5:38</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of Jesus Christ to himself</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:36\">JHN 5:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:14\">JHN 8:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:13\">JHN 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:11\">JHN 14:11</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of Jesus Christ's miracles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:11\">JHN 14:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:25\">JHN 10:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:24\">JHN 15:24</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of the first Christians</h2>\n<h3>Commissioned by Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:17-Matt10:20\">MAT 10:17–10:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12-Luke21:13\">LUK 21:12–21:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:18-Acts4:21\">ACT 4:18–4:21</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:1-Luke1:2\">LUK 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:48\">LUK 24:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:27\">JHN 15:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:21-Acts1:22\">ACT 1:21–1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:33\">ACT 4:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:31\">ACT 13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:5-Acts9:6\">ACT 9:5–9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:14-Acts22:15\">ACT 22:14–22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">ACT 23:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:16\">ACT 26:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3\">HEB 2:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16\">2PE 1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1\">1JN 1:1</a></p>\n<h2>The witness of converts</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15-1Pet3:16\">1PE 3:15–3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:8</a></p>",
